## Bug Status Legend

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| Open | Bug documented, not yet fixed |
| In Progress | Fix being developed |
| Fixed | Fix complete, awaiting verification |
| Verified | Fix verified in testing |
| Closed | Resolved and released |
| Won't Fix | Intentionally not fixing |

