## Bug File Structure

Each bug should have its own file: `BUG-NNN-brief-title.md`

Example:
```
.agent/bugs/
├── README.md                    # This file
├── images/                      # Screenshots for all bugs
│   ├── bug-001-error-screen.png
│   └── bug-002-wrong-layout.png
├── BUG-001-login-fails.md
├── BUG-002-missing-button.md
└── BUG-003-slow-load.md
```

